<h1>New Host Notification</h1>

<p>
  Dear <%= @organisation.contact_name %>,
</p>
<p>
  Your organisation <%= @organisation.name %> new host participant has been created in MOBEEAS, waiting for your approval.
  This user would like to apply for HOST level, have the ability to create opportunity and request the use of company's token from Admin Hosts.
  Here is your new host details in MOBEEAS:
<p>

<p>
  <strong>Name:</strong>
  <%= @user.org_user_profile.name %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Phone:</strong>
  <%= @user.org_user_profile.phone %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Email:</strong>
  <%= @user.email %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Position:</strong>
  <%= @user.org_user_profile.position %>
</p>

<p>
  If you approve <%= @user.org_user_profile.name %> to be the admin host of your organisation, please click the link below.
  Thank you.
</p>

<% @org_user = OrgUser.find_by(user_id: @user.id, organisation_id: @organisation.id) %>
<p><%= link_to 'Approve '+@user.org_user_profile.name, verified_host_org_user_url(@org_user.id, org_id: @organisation.id) %></p>
